  "headline": "Mental Health Basics",
  "description": "Mental health encompasses emotional, psychological, and social well-being. Common conditions: anxiety disorders (most common, 19% of adults), depression, bipolar disorder, PTSD, OCD, schizophrenia (~1%). Treatment: psychotherapy (CBT, DBT), medication, lifestyle changes. Early intervention improves outcomes. Mental health is health — no stigma.",
